== 影响 ==
受风暴的前身低气压区影响，牙买加从11月5日就开始降下暴雨。之后随气旋增强和逼近，该国又降下更多雨量。11月5至11日，[[京斯敦|京斯敦]]的降雨量高达773毫米。银山种植园降水更多，11月5至9日共有2908毫米，11月4至11日更高达3429毫米。<ref name="pmp" />暴雨引发重大洪灾，约有50万香蕉植株被洪水摧毁，占该国总量约五分之一<ref name="Partagás" />{{rp|20}}。金斯敦附近的水厂被毁，多条隧道和铁路因[[山崩|山体滑坡]]阻塞，许多桥梁和公路受损或被毁，导致众多城镇同外界的交通中断，救灾工作也受到影响。[[安诺托贝|安诺托贝]]的洪水有近一米深。<ref name="WH1">{{cite news |author = Press Association | work = Wanganui Herald | date = 1909-11-15 | title = Hurricane In Jamaica | page = 5}}</ref>牙买加各地的洪灾共导致30人死亡，损失数额估计达700万美元<ref name="NYT1">{{cite news | author = W. J. Gardiner | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | date = 1909-11-27 | title = A Stormy Island And Its History | page = BR744}}</ref>。洪灾过后，该国政府拨款约15万美元用于修复损伤<ref name="WH1" />。

邻近的海地也降下瓢泼大雨，引发重大洪灾<ref name="Partagás" />{{rp|20}}。降雨量据报超过610毫米<ref name="TLDS1">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = The Lewiston Daily Sun | date = 1909-11-10 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=yaggAAAAIBAJ&sjid=XGkFAAAAIBAJ&dq=haiti%20hurricane&pg=1323%2C2972932 | page = 9 | accessdate = 2016-12-15 | title = No Word Received}}</ref>，在该国各地引起山体滑坡和大面积洪灾<ref name="Partagás" />{{rp|20}}。由于大部分道路不是被毁便是被淹，海地的初步灾情报告无法及时经新闻媒体披露。飓风过去数天后，才开始有报导称风暴对该国造成重大破坏。[[戈纳伊夫|戈纳伊夫]]附近的河流泛滥成灾，全城都被淹没，居民只能躲到楼上或屋顶。城内一座桥梁被汹涌的河水吞没，导致16人遇难。[[太子港|太子港]]附近也有河流泛滥成灾，将就近区域淹没。<ref name="NYT2">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = The New York Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161215145151/http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1909/11/14/101031224.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1481813770&Signature=vng0vxePNZnU4tzXi5zrn9NoGjc%3D | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-12-15 | title = Hurricane In Haiti Did Great Damage | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-12-15 | url = http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1909/11/14/101031224.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1481813770&Signature=vng0vxePNZnU4tzXi5zrn9NoGjc%3D | page = C2 | date = 1909-11-14 }}</ref>

亚基河（{{lang|en|Yaqui River}}）沿线爆发史无前例的洪灾，因此还形成估计长达48公里，深24米的大湖。洪水将许多村庄摧毁，预计有成百上千人遇难<ref name="GT1" />。但由于缺乏灾后统计，海地能够确定的经济损失仅有300万美元，估计实际数值要高得多<ref name="NYT3">{{cite news | author = Alexander E. Barthe | newspaper = The New York Times | date = 1909-11-25 | accessdate = 2016-12-15 | title = The West Indian Sufferers | format = PDF | page = 10 | url = http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1909/11/25/101906638.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1481813815&Signature=VforZvEpxcXwFUrv2abshBUcx6Q%3D}}</ref>。该国经确定有166人死亡<ref name="BasinDeadliest">{{cite web | author1 = Edward N. Rappaport | author2 = Jose Fernandez-Partagas | author3 = Jack L. Beven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1997-04-22 | accessdate = 2016-12-15 | title = The Deadliest Atlantic Tropical Cyclones, 1492-1996 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadlyapp1.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-09-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160907054020/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadlyapp1.shtml | deadurl = no }}</ref>，但也有多份报导认为海地可能有数百人丧生<ref name="GT1">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Gettysburg Times | date = 1909-11-23 | accessdate = 2016-12-15 | title = Hundreds Killed In Haiti | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=QaslAAAAIBAJ&sjid=OPwFAAAAIBAJ&dq=haiti%20hurricane&pg=3241%2C3746512 | page = 2}}</ref>。确认的死者大部分来自西北省，共有150人<ref name="HaitiDisasterList">{{cite web | publisher = Ayitigouvenans | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2012-03-06 | title = January 12 Earthquake in Haiti | url = http://www.ayitigouvenans.org/January%2012%20Earthquake%20in%20Haiti.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120306155634/http://www.ayitigouvenans.org/January%2012%20Earthquake%20in%20Haiti.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-03-06 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

